9:"post_type";s:7:"project";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:5;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:1748;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2015-09-01 07:36:58";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2015-09-01 07:36:58";s:12:"post_content";s:0:"";s:10:"post_title";s:19:"Qurban, Urban Style";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:449:"Dengan pengalaman lebih dari 3 tahun kami dapat menjadi pilihan terpercaya anda untuk melakukan qurban, aqiqah, dan sedekah domba.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nUrbanQurban adalah platform yang membantu kaum urban untuk bisa melakukan qurban, aqiqah, dan sedekah domba.\r\n\r\nUrbanQurban menghubungkan antara kaum urban dengan masyarakat marginal di seluruh Indonesia sehingga penyebaran qurban, aqiqah, maupun sedekah domba menjadi lebih mudah, terpercaya, dan merata.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:18:"qurban-urban-style";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-09-04 08:37:46";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-09-04 08:37:46";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:52:"http://localhost/badr/?post_type=project&#038;p=1748";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:7:"project";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";s:6:"filter";s:3:"raw";}i:6;O:7:"WP_Post":24:{s:2:"ID";i:2973;s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2015-09-03 05:42:51";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2015-09-03 05:42:51";s:12:"post_content";s:0:"";s:10:"post_title";s:28:"Learn to Read Quran Fluently";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:1790:"Learning how to recite the Quran is now easier than ever! Learn Quran provides comprehensive lessons ranging from very basic topics (The Alphabet, Harakaat, etc.) to advanced Tajweed lessons, making this app suitable for learners at all levels.\r\n\r\nLearn Quran is designed so you can learn with a teacher or by yourself. It''s your Quran learning guide.\r\n\r\nCONTENTS:\r\n1. THEORY: Learn the topic using words taken from the Quran.\r\n2. PRACTICE: Master the topic by practicing what you’ve learned (using Quranic examples).\r\n3. TEST: Measure your comprehension by testing what you’ve learned (again based on words from the Quran).\r\n\r\nFEATURES:\r\n• VOICE: Voice narration of the Arabic words, making learning simple.\r\n• TRANSLITERATION (can be turned on/off): Transliteration of the Arabic text, making reading easy. The transliterations are based on UNESCO\r\n• RECORDING: Voice recording to allow you to compare your recitation to the voice-over, making it easy to measure how much you’ve learnt.\r\n\r\nLearn Quran features Haafiz Muhammad S. Bashir as the voice-over. He is the first winner of the International Competition on Quran (Kuwait, 2014) and a teacher of various Quran classes. We want you to learn from the best.\r\n\r\nDISCLAIMER\r\nOur reason for locking some of the content in the free version: We hire professional developers (whose services are expensive) and our resources are limited. We apologize for our limitations. Please make dua that one day Allah enables us to provide Islamic applications for free.\r\n\r\nP.S. If you find any errors, the best way to give feedback is by sending an email (as opposed to writing a review). This guarantees your feedback will reach the right person inshaaAllah.\r\n\r\nCP: <a href="mailto:sani@badr-interactive.com">sani@badr-interactive.com</a>";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:6:"closed";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:28:"learn-to-read-quran-fluently";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2015-09-04 08:37:32";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2015-09-04 08:37:32";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";i:0;s:4:"guid";s:52:"http://localhost/badr/?post_type=project&#038;p=2973";s:10:"menu_order";i:0;s:9:"post_type";s:7:"project";s:14:"